{"tid":872216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Panasonic 旗下公司推出「馬眼罩」內建藍牙耳機，提升工作專注力","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:33:47.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"793fa808e09bb5a7c1b1eec7e2c3e932f4394e66","tid":872216,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"相信現在許多人都會選擇到像是咖啡廳等地開放式空間工作，當然在外難免會受到些旁人活動所影響。例如在咖啡廳工作時，隔壁桌聊天、走動等活動。不過現在Panasonic 旗下公司在近期推出一款造型類似於馬眼罩的產品 Wear Space ，讓使用者可以在公共場合中，持續保有高專注力繼續工作奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/220303_b22367526a2f783a10e7febf575ba690.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F220303_b22367526a2f783a10e7febf575ba690.png&h=54c5e15d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這款外觀類似於馬眼罩造型的遮蔽式眼罩 Wear Space ，由Panasonic的設計工作室未來生活工廠（ Future Life Factory ），為了解決在開放空間受到兩側視線的干擾，提升專注力和工作效率。這原理也確實與騎馬時有些雷同，當初為了讓其實避免馬匹分心，將馬的眼睛周圍使用黑布遮蔽兩側的餘光，讓馬匹能專注於眼前的視線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/220339_d3c6f1a7a361d882a80b8588473fb9a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F220339_d3c6f1a7a361d882a80b8588473fb9a5.png&h=63f6ed5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWear Space 可以將兩側的視線遮蔽住，配戴方式與傳統耳罩式耳機不太相同，由內側兩邊的固定設計固定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/220415_fda25e3dc4e0bd2976014abfa9746ccb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F220415_fda25e3dc4e0bd2976014abfa9746ccb.png&h=ccb5be44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWear Space 除了能透過視線提升時者的專注力。在聲音方面，也內建了藍牙耳機，不只能播放音樂、亦同時可支援降噪功能，讓使用者配戴 Wear Space 就像是一只造型特殊的降噪耳機，在周圍環境聲音的消除後，不受噪音干擾更能再將專注力提高。<br />\n <br />\n另外，可透過手機專屬 App 隨時控制 Wear Space 降噪的效果，目前這款 App 仍在開發階段。<br />\n <br />\n售價方面， Wear Space 在日本群募網站 Green Funding 募資中，早鳥價為 29,000 日圓（約合新台幣 8,000元），預計總共需募資金額 1,500 萬日圓，目前距離截止前達到 896萬日圓，完成度約 59% 。如順利達標，預計於 2019 年 8 月前寄出。"},{"pid":"ff8ee2dc8760717ff300073cae0426255baa4b54","tid":872216,"uid":33698,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"仲以為係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8ddaa4125d445d22354ae376981350be9e46bd","tid":872216,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442b97b4ed4e0505eea18ba0e1db8e676a69ea65","tid":872216,"uid":60412,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"馬眼 罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356ec81bdc8046b711805d2a6c827ff6913094c0","tid":872216,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"仲諗住 馬眼係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc39288b6b0e323c5588d1230e2e4677c92df5","tid":872216,"uid":61331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"愚人節咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59b57b07e6ebd1c32744fa0be9f1ecec1944451","tid":872216,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl